{"id":1735070,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:14.745Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735070,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Katakan Tidak Pada Cinta","overview":"The story follows Diyana, who works as an interior designer and moves to a new company. There she reunites with Zarin, a senior interior designer with whom she had previously fought due to a misunderstanding. Since then, they have constantly quarreled and cannot work together. This worries Firman, the company owner and also Zarin's friend. Firman arranges a plan for Zarin and Diyana to reconcile by sending them both to work on a project in Melaka. Firman also instructs Latif and Mariam to assist Zarin and Diyana. Latif and Mariam are also tasked as spies for Firman. Both of them agree to cooperate in mending the relationship between Zarin and Diyana. While in Melaka, Zarin and Diyana continue to quarrel until an incident occurs where Diyana enters the forest alone and is followed by Zarin. When Diyana becomes frightened because the tree is swaying, she flees and collides with Zarin. They both continue running and fall into a dark hole. Various incidents of fighting between them occur.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/umaMMKPwwO8lalyeNdFduHN1CWj.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2017-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Katakan Tidak Pada Cinta","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1283207,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Azrel Ismail","original_name":"Azrel Ismail","popularity":0.2385,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5eb3bf64a9e69183922433","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1742583,"known_for_department":"Acting","name"